    <div>In this tutorial we would learn how to make dropdown multi-columns menu in drupal. We are going to be making use of the <a href="https://drupal.org/project/tb_megamenu">TB Mega Menu</a>. This menu is the perfect choice for creating unique menus in drupal. With this menu, you don't need any coding experience. All you simply need do is make use of the innovative back-end user interface. With this module it is so easy creating menus with multi-columns that can contain drupal block, images, links, e.t.c.</div>
<div> </div>
<div>This module is still in dev version, however, it works like a dream. Consider this module a gift to the drupal community. It is very different from any drupal menu module you have come across.</div>
